  "title": "Marketing Executive (Paya Lebar) (Education Sector) #NKC",
  "description": "<p><p>Support the planning and execution of marketing campaigns.</p></p><p><p>Research industry trends and prepare high-quality drafts or copy for social media posts, promotional emails, and other marketing materials.</p></p><p><p>Design or assist in creating written, video, and visual content for marketing channels to promote the company and its products.</p></p><p><p>Manage social media channels including Instagram, Facebook, Xiao Hong Shu, WeChat, and TikTok; respond to customer inquiries as needed.</p></p><p><p>Ensure all marketing materials adhere to branding guidelines.</p></p><p><p>Plan and execute customer engagement initiatives, such as community events or fireside chats, via WhatsApp and other channels.</p></p><p><p>Organize lead generation events in collaboration with key partners.</p></p><p><p>Monitor, measure, and report on the effectiveness of marketing campaigns, social media ads, and other initiatives.</p></p><p><p>Assist with ad-hoc administrative or data entry tasks as requested by management.</p></p><p><p>Lead offline marketing efforts, including banners, pillar ads, and exhibitions.<br /></p><p><br /></p><p>Interested applicants may email resume to kellychooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Chooi Kelly (CEI Registration No: R25136207)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (EA: 99C4599)</p><p></p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted</p><p><br /></p></p>",
